# Firebase config (google-services.json)
# Note: this file CONTAINS the FCM project_number and an api_key, but those
# values are CLIENT-side identifiers that ship inside every published APK
# anyway. It is safe to commit — and EAS Build requires it to be tracked by
# git in order to upload it during prebuild. We commit it so Android FCM
# can initialize properly.
# google-services.json   ← DO NOT re-add this line
GoogleService-Info.plist
